info.author: Leif Johnson
info.description:
# py-tagger

A Python library for tagging sequences (of words, letters, numbers, events,
etc.) with labels (part of speech, phoneme, other numbers, etc.).

## Installation

With `pip`

    pip install lmj.tagger
